title: Uncanny X-Men - Rise and Fall of the Shi'ar Empire (Dgtl-TPB)
description: After the controversial storyline of X-Men: Deadly Genesis (utter shit in my opinion, so I did not post it), Ed Brubaker returns to the pages of X-Men to deal with the fallout of his new creation - Vulcan, the powerful third Summers brother. This time, however, his target is the Shi'ar, and much conflict ensues. Collects Uncanny X-Men 475-486. All credit to the original scanners, please seed and enjoy.
